    "en": {
      "title": "The state of emergency is out this week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe said that the current state of emergency will be lifted by the end of this week.",
        "The President said that the country is currently at a stable level and accordingly said that there is no need to extend the state of emergency.",
        "The President stated this while addressing the \"Conference of Academic Professionals Associations - 2022\" awards ceremony held at the Cinnamon Lakeside Hotel, Colombo today (16)."
      ],
